or complete research question specification - cannot proceed without defined research scope",\n    "alternatives": [],\n    "not_recommended": [\n      "Attempting to guess the intended research topic",\n      "Proceeding with generic research methodology overview"\n    ]\n  },\n  "gaps": [\n    "Actual research question or topic",\n    "Required deliverables or output format",\n    "Time constraints or deadlines",\n    "Available resources or data sources",\n    "Success criteria for research phase"\n  ],\n  "sources": [\n    "Provided dispatcher output JSON",\n    "Provided subtask JSON"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## Context: subtask\n```json\n{\n  "id": 2,\n  "assigned_agent": "builder",\n  "description": "Builder phase for: ...",\n  "depends_on": [\n    1\n  ],\n  "approval_level": 0\n}\n```\n\n## Context: worktree_path\n```json\n"/mnt/c/Users/user/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/worktrees/smoke-021"\n```\n\n## Context: revision_feedback\n```json\n{\n  "attempt": 1,\n  "prior_verdict": "FAIL",\n  "failed_criteria": [],\n  "findings": [\n    {\n      "id": 1,\n      "severity": "critical",\n      "file": "N/A",\n      "issue": "Task specification incomplete - description contains placeholder text \'...\' preventing any implementation",\n      "suggestion": "Dispatcher must provide complete task specification with clear deliverables and requirements"\n    },\n    {\n      "id": 2,\n      "severity": "critical",\n      "file": "N/A",\n      "issue": "Builder correctly escalated rather than guessing requirements, resulting in no deliverables",\n      "suggestion": "Resolve upstream task definition before attempting review"\n    },\n    {\n      "id": 3,\n      "severity": "major",\n      "file": "N/A",\n      "issue": "Research phase also identified incomplete specification but workflow continued",\n      "suggestion": "Implement workflow halt mechanism when critical specification gaps are identified"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text'